# Version Bump Reminder
# Always bump version in package.json and update CHANGELOG.md before committing
# Version format: MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH (e.g., 1.0.2)
# 
# Steps:
# 1. Update version in package.json
# 2. Add entry to CHANGELOG.md
# 3. Run: npm run build && cp dist/mushroom.js .
# 4. Commit with message: "Version X.Y.Z: Description"
# 5. Create tag: git tag -a vX.Y.Z -m "Version X.Y.Z: Description"
# 6. Push: git push origin main --tags
# 7. Create GitHub release with the built mushroom.js file

